            explanation: "Decode with -3: V→S, Q→N, R→O, Z→W. The word is SNOW. ✓"
          },
          // Code ORYH was made with +3. Decode: O(15)-3=L(12), R(18)-3=O(15), Y(25)-3=V(22), H(8)-3=E(5) = LOVE
          {
